<text>%3CTEXTFORMAT%20LEADING%3D%222%22%3E%3CP%20ALIGN%3D%22LEFT%22%3E%3CFONT%20FACE%3D%22Georgia%22%20SIZE%3D%2212%22%20COLOR%3D%22%23000000%22%20LETTERSPACING%3D%220%22%20KERNING%3D%220%22%3E%3CB%3EComplimentary%20shuttle%20service%20to%20all%20downtown%20venues%20%3C%2FB%3E%20Detroit%20Location%20Only%3C%2FFONT%3E%3C%2FP%3E%3C%2FTEXTFORMAT%3E%3CTEXTFORMAT%20LEADING%3D%222%22%3E%3CP%20ALIGN%3D%22LEFT%22%3E%3CFONT%20FACE%3D%22Georgia%22%20SIZE%3D%2212%22%20COLOR%3D%22%23000000%22%20LETTERSPACING%3D%220%22%20KERNING%3D%220%22%3E%3C%2FFONT%3E%3C%2FP%3E%3C%2FTEXTFORMAT%3E%3CTEXTFORMAT%20LEADING%3D%222%22%3E%3CP%20ALIGN%3D%22LEFT%22%3E%3CFONT%20FACE%3D%22Georgia%22%20SIZE%3D%2212%22%20COLOR%3D%22%23000000%22%20LETTERSPACING%3D%220%22%20KERNING%3D%220%22%3EThis%20isn%E2%80%99t%20retro%2C%20this%20is%20real.%20%20We%E2%80%99ve%20been%20around%20since%201948.%20%20There%20aren%E2%80%99t%20many%20restaurants%20with%20this%20kind%20of%20character.%20%20One%20step%20inside%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20see%20that%20this%20is%20a%20place%20that%20time%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20touch.%20%20We%20like%20to%20keep%20it%20that%20way.%20%20From%20our%20service%20to%20our%20cuisine%20you%E2%80%99ll%20feel%20right%20at%20home%20in%20our%20warm%2C%20elegant%2C%20and%20traditional%20atmosphere.%20%20If%20you%20like%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20wait%20until%20you%20taste%20our%20food.%20%3C%2FFONT%3E%3C%2FP%3E%3C%2FTEXTFORMAT%3E%3CTEXTFORMAT%20LEADING%3D%222%22%3E%3CP%20ALIGN%3D%22LEFT%22%3E%3CFONT%20FACE%3D%22Georgia%22%20SIZE%3D%2212%22%20COLOR%3D%22%23000000%22%20LETTERSPACING%3D%220%22%20KERNING%3D%220%22%3E%3C%2FFONT%3E%3C%2FP%3E%3C%2FTEXTFORMAT%3E%3CTEXTFORMAT%20LEADING%3D%222%22%3E%3CP%20ALIGN%3D%22LEFT%22%3E%3CFONT%20FACE%3D%22Georgia%22%20SIZE%3D%2212%22%20COLOR%3D%22%23000000%22%20LETTERSPACING%3D%220%22%20KERNING%3D%220%22%3EMario%26apos%3Bs%20has%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20last%20existing%20supper%20clubs%20of%20its%20era.%20It%26apos%3Bs%20an%20unpretentious%2C%20old-school%20kind%20of%20cool.%20%20The%20type%20of%20Italian%20joint%20where%20you%26apos%3Bre%20served%20a%20vegetable%20and%20relish%20tray%20as%20soon%20as%20you%20sit%20down.%20%3C%2FFONT%3E%3C%2FP%3E%3C%2FTEXTFORMAT%3E%3CTEXTFORMAT%20LEADING%3D%222%22%3E%3CP%20ALIGN%3D%22LEFT%22%3E%3CFONT%20FACE%3D%22Georgia%22%20SIZE%3D%2212%22%20COLOR%3D%22%23000000%22%20LETTERSPACING%3D%220%22%20KERNING%3D%220%22%3E%3C%2FFONT%3E%3C%2FP%3E%3C%2FTEXTFORMAT%3E%3CTEXTFORMAT%20LEADING%3D%222%22%3E%3CP%20ALIGN%3D%22LEFT%22%3E%3CFONT%20FACE%3D%22Georgia%22%20SIZE%3D%2212%22%20COLOR%3D%22%23000000%22%20LETTERSPACING%3D%220%22%20KERNING%3D%220%22%3EMario%26apos%3Bs%20provides%20a%20truly%20unique%20dining%20experience%20with%20tableside%20cooking%2C%20astounding%20service%2C%20valet%20parking%20and%20ballroom%20dancing%20on%20the%20weekends.%20Since%20it%26apos%3Bs%20close%20to%20the%20Theater%20District%2C%20Mario%26apos%3Bs%20is%20a%20great%20place%20to%20dine%20before%20or%20after%20a%20show.%20In%20fact%2C%20shuttles%20are%20offered%20to%20select%20locations.%20%3C%2FFONT%3E%3C%2FP%3E%3C%2FTEXTFORMAT%3E%3CTEXTFORMAT%20LEADING%3D%222%22%3E%3CP%20ALIGN%3D%22LEFT%22%3E%3CFONT%20FACE%3D%22Georgia%22%20SIZE%3D%2212%22%20COLOR%3D%22%23000000%22%20LETTERSPACING%3D%220%22%20KERNING%3D%220%22%3E%3C%2FFONT%3E%3C%2FP%3E%3C%2FTEXTFORMAT%3E%3CTEXTFORMAT%20LEADING%3D%222%22%3E%3CP%20ALIGN%3D%22LEFT%22%3E%3CFONT%20FACE%3D%22Georgia%22%20SIZE%3D%2212%22%20COLOR%3D%22%230000FF%22%20LETTERSPACING%3D%220%22%20KERNING%3D%220%22%3E%3CA%20HREF%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdetroitmarios%22%20TARGET%3D%22%22%3EClick%20here%20to%20visit%20our%20Facebook%20page%3C%2FA%3E%3CFONT%20COLOR%3D%22%23000000%22%3E%3C%2FFONT%3E%3C%2FFONT%3E%3C%2FP%3E%3C%2FTEXTFORMAT%3E%3CTEXTFORMAT%20LEADING%3D%222%22%3E%3CP%20ALIGN%3D%22LEFT%22%3E%3CFONT%20FACE%3D%22Georgia%22%20SIZE%3D%2212%22%20COLOR%3D%22%23000000%22%20LETTERSPACING%3D%220%22%20KERNING%3D%220%22%3E%3C%2FFONT%3E%3C%2FP%3E%3C%2FTEXTFORMAT%3E%3CTEXTFORMAT%20LEADING%3D%222%22%3